<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-37-1130 </DOCNO><TEXT>The work reported herein illustrates the ability of a lamellar solid toserve as a medium for a classical analytical titration and to act asa chemical sensor. The reaction of AgUP and HCN gas is described in detailhere. The reaction yields a solid that emits the characteristic yellow-greencolor of HUP. 15 references, 1 figure, 1 table.</TEXT></DOC>